{"tid":2398921,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"工作要求：擁護一國兩制、遵守香港基本法","createTime":"2021-02-07T16:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T04:18:46.000Z","uid":112747,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4711f495d2cc7fbd285bf74696ea1429194d607a","tid":2398921,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:58:56.000Z","msg":"唔知駛唔駛宣誓呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.jobsdb.com/hk/en/job/job-100003008204170\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.jobsdb.com%2Fhk%2Fen%2Fjob%2Fjob-100003008204170&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=dd85f071\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.jobsdb.com/hk/en/job/job-100003008204170</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.jobsdb.com/hk/en/job/job-100003008204083\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.jobsdb.com%2Fhk%2Fen%2Fjob%2Fjob-100003008204083&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=8df9efcd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.jobsdb.com/hk/en/job/job-100003008204083</a>"},{"pid":"1dfabe649e498893fc9862d558037d835a734b06","tid":2398921,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:59:25.000Z","msg":"人力資源助理（人力資源部）<br />\nChina Power International Holding Limited<br />\nCentral &amp; Western Area<br />\nSalary negotiable<br />\nPosted on 03 Feb 2021<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人力資源助理（人力資源部）<br />\nChina Power International Holding Limited<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJob Highlights<br />\n擁護一國兩制、遵守香港基本法。具有香港籍。<br />\n具有全日制大學本科及以上學歷，2019或2020年大學畢業，人力資源管理專業畢業生優先。<br />\n能將英語、漢語作為工作語言。<br />\n<br />\nJob Description<br />\n崗位職責：協助完成公司香港本部人資事務工作等，工作期限為1年"},{"pid":"2b9511df24964ba522e6af38574491de9fd95e7b","tid":2398921,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:59:42.000Z","msg":"商務助理（项目開發部）<br />\nChina Power International Holding Limited<br />\nCentral &amp; Western Area<br />\nSalary negotiable<br />\nPosted on 03 Feb 2021<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJob Highlights<br />\n擁護一國兩制、遵守香港基本法，具有香港籍。<br />\n具有全日制大學本科及以上學歷，2019或2020年大學畢業，商務管理專業畢業生優先。<br />\n能將英語、漢語作為工作語言。<br />\n<br />\nJob Description<br />\n協助完成公司香港本部商務工作等，工作期限為1年"},{"pid":"914b533a80be221060c09cc048f15832a9934d8a","tid":2398921,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:59:55.000Z","msg":"Company Overview<br />\n中国电力国际有限公司（简称&ldquo;中电国际&rdquo;）于1994年经国务院批准在香港注册成立，是原电力部境外融资的窗口企业，1998年改组为国家电力公司的全资子公司。2002年按照国家电力体制改革统一部署，以中电国际为核心资产成立中国电力投资集团公司（简称&ldquo;中电投&rdquo;）。2004年中电国际以优质核心资产为主设立中国电力国际发展有限公司（简称&ldquo;中国电力&rdquo;），同年中国电力在香港联交所上市,<a href=\"http://股票代码2380.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%812380.HK&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=62d7a750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">股票代码2380.HK</a>，是五大发电集团首家红筹上市公司,也是目前水电比例最高的境外上市公司。2015年中电投与国家核电重组为国家电力投资集团公司，中电国际成为国家电投集团的重要骨干企业。2019年，国家电投重组中电国际与海外公司，中电国际成为集团公司境外发展的主力平台，旨在打造国际化发展和投资的核心竞争能力，专注于境外市场开发和境外项目投资。"},{"pid":"c50ece482cb02131e8837c849b366ff19f19af1c","tid":2398921,"uid":16164,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T17:05:47.000Z","msg":"香港係地區唔係國家<br />\n&ldquo;香港藉&rdquo;已經意圖顛覆國家政權 分裂國家<br />\n報國安<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a06bdd40657a8487e8c33f1e14ece9ec908d78d","tid":2398921,"uid":167928,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T17:09:16.000Z","msg":"咱家都是中国人！中国籍！香港籍就是搞港独！"},{"pid":"7799815e8a821cabfaf09a7d61c527e255107186","tid":2398921,"uid":211466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T17:10:55.000Z","msg":"又唔係不得有外藉<br />\n把撚"},{"pid":"ede0df5da7d961d2fee02478498478ce8a393b86","tid":2398921,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T22:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\